There are many VIM short cuts
To set the swap file in to a back up directory.
In .vimrc dir set these lines
set backup
set backupdir=~/.vim/backup
set directory=~/.vim/tmp
set spell
syntax on
colorscheme delek

create a .vim/backup and .vim/tmp dirs
create a .vim/colors
To get more colors in to vim
create .vim/colors dir
clone all the colors from git
git clone https://github.com/flazz/vim-colorschemes.git
